profile:
We take pride in doing the small, odd jobs around your home or business that other companies may not want to do.  As a handyman company, we currently operate in Halifax, Nova Scotia.
Using the experience gained over 16 + years doing home renovations and repairs, we aim to help homeowners maintain and update their homes.  After all, most people have more important things to concentrate on than that bathtub re-chalking or fixing that squeaky door that always jams.

For your ease of mind, we are fully covered by liability insurance and the Workers Compensation Board of Nova Scotia.
